strings: <voice_0x01000EE1><se_def>The prince Carlos: The hunchback How do you escape? That lizard didn't know me very well, so he left his boring job and went back to the castle!
<voice_0x01000EE2><se_def>The prince Carlos: Imagine if the prime minister told me to stay behind him so I wouldn't be scared.
<voice_0x01000EE3><se_def>The prince Carlos: If you continue to cheat, we will keep them away. Even if you call me later, I won't go.
<voice_0x01000EE4><se_def>The prince Carlos: said <leader>! How many times must I say that if I don't catch him he will run away!
<voice_0x01000EE5><se_def>The prince Carlos: Didn't you hear after this
<voice_0x01000EE6><se_def>The prince Carlos: once Don't let them fool you! Walk quietly in the back! S-L-O-W-L-Y behind you know! - it gets worse! until then
<voice_0x01000EE7><se_def>The prince Carlos: I didn't expect ordinary people to be so stupid! This you will never understand, this time listen carefully to the voice of the teacher!
<voice_0x01000EE8><se_def>The prince Carlos: You have to walk backwards slowly. What you shouldn't do is bang your head hard. short path! Really?
